### **Capital Raising Announcement Summary**  
- **Structure**: Placement  
- **Total Securities Issued**: 212,790,697 ordinary shares (CY5)  
- **Issue Price**: AUD 0.086 per share  
- **Capital Raised**: ~AUD 18.3 million (212,790,697 × 0.086)  
- **Placement Breakdown**:  
  - 15% capacity (LR 7.1): 126,025,591 shares  
  - 10% capacity (LR 7.1A): 84,925,316 shares  
- **Proposed Issue Date**: 27 June 2025  
- **Shareholder Approval Required**: Yes (for 1,162,790 director-linked shares; deadline 29 Aug 2025)  
- **Use of Proceeds**:  
  - Chibougamau Copper-Gold Project (exploration, studies, permitting)  
  - Working capital & placement costs  
- **Lead Managers**: Canaccord Genuity & Euroz Hartleys (5% fee).  
- **Underwritten**: No
